methods.getVolSurfaceExpirations:
Gets an array of expirations associated with the vol surface.

:return: (io.deephaven.db.tables.utils.DBDateTime[]) array of expirations associated with the vol surface.
methods.getVolSurfaceForwardErrors:
Gets the forward price errors associated with the expirations in the vol surface.

:return: (double[]) forward price errors associated with the expirations in the vol surface.
methods.getVolSurfaceForwardPrices:
Gets the forward prices associated with the expirations in the vol surface.

:return: (double[]) forward prices associated with the expirations in the vol surface.
methods.getVolSurfaceImpliedVolErrors:
Gets the implied vol errors of the vol surface.  The first index corresponds to the expiration.

:return: (double[][]) implied vol errors of the vol surface.
methods.getVolSurfaceImpliedVols:
Gets the implied vols of the vol surface.  The first index corresponds to the expiration.

:return: (double[][]) implied vols of the vol surface.
methods.getVolSurfaceStrikes:
Gets the strikes of the vol surface.  The first index corresponds to the expiration.

:return: (double[][]) strikes of the vol surface.
methods.setVolSurfaceExpirations:
Sets an array of expirations associated with the vol surface.

:param volSurfaceExpirations: (io.deephaven.db.tables.utils.DBDateTime[]) - array of expirations associated with the vol surface.
methods.setVolSurfaceForwardErrors:
Sets the forward price errors associated with the expirations in the vol surface.

:param volSurfaceForwardErrors: (double[]) - forward price errors associated with the expirations in the vol surface.
methods.setVolSurfaceForwardPrices:
Sets the forward prices associated with the expirations in the vol surface.

:param volSurfaceForwardPrices: (double[]) - forward prices associated with the expirations in the vol surface.
methods.setVolSurfaceImpliedVolErrors:
Sets the implied vol errors of the vol surface.  The first index corresponds to the expiration.

:param volSurfaceImpliedVolErrors: (double[][]) - implied vol errors of the vol surface.
methods.setVolSurfaceImpliedVols:
Sets the implied vols of the vol surface.  The first index corresponds to the expiration.

:param volSurfaceImpliedVols: (double[][]) - implied vols of the vol surface.
methods.setVolSurfaceStrikes:
Sets the strikes of the vol surface.  The first index corresponds to the expiration.

:param volSurfaceStrikes: (double[][]) - strikes of the vol surface.

text: A snapshot of market data needed to fit a futures option model.  Option prices are provided as a vol surface.
